    <item>
      <title>拜登将禁止在美国大西洋和太平洋大片水域进行新的石油钻探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/biden-to-ban-new-oil-drilling-over-vast-stretch-of-us-atlantic-pacific-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将下令禁止在美国沿海约 6.25 亿英亩的面积上进行新的海上石油和天然气开发，并禁止出售大西洋和太平洋水域以及墨西哥湾东部的钻探权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/biden-to-ban-new-oil-drilling-over-vast-stretch-of-us-atlantic-pacific-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 04:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国电动汽车销量激增，汽车制造商纷纷降价以躲避罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/ev-sales-surge-in-uk-as-carmakers-slash-prices-to-dodge-fines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于汽车制造商不断削减插电式车型的价格以避免罚款，上个月在英国注册的新车中几乎有三分之一是全电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/ev-sales-surge-in-uk-as-carmakers-slash-prices-to-dodge-fines</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
